<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Widget Component Demo</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        /* Enabel Bootstrap Theme Widget Styles */
        .widget {
            background: #fff;
            border: 1px solid #dee2e6;
            border-radius: 0.375rem;
            padding: 1.25rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            box-shadow: 0 0.125rem 0.25rem rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.075);
        }
        
        .widget:hover {
            box-shadow: 0 0.5rem 1rem rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }
        
        .widget-link {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: inherit;
        }
        
        .widget-link:hover {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: inherit;
        }
        
        .widget-icon {
            font-size: 3rem;
            margin-right: 1rem;
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }
        
        .widget-content {
            flex-grow: 1;
        }
        
        .widget-content .count {
            font-size: 2rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin: 0 0 0.25rem 0;
        }
        
        .widget-content p {
            margin: 0;
            color: #6c757d;
            font-size: 0.875rem;
        }
        
        /* Variant Colors */
        .widget-primary {
            border-left: 4px solid #007bff;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(0, 123, 255, 0.1) 0%, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9) 100%);
        }
        
        .widget-primary .widget-icon {
            color: #007bff;
        }
        
        .widget-primary .count {
            color: #007bff;
        }
        
        .widget-secondary {
            border-left: 4px solid #6c757d;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(108, 117, 125, 0.1) 0%, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9) 100%);
        }
        
        .widget-secondary .widget-icon {
            color: #6c757d;
        }
        
        .widget-secondary .count {
            color: #6c757d;
        }
        
        .widget-success {
            border-left: 4px solid #28a745;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(40, 167, 69, 0.1) 0%, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9) 100%);
        }
        
        .widget-success .widget-icon {
            color: #28a745;
        }
        
        .widget-success .count {
            color: #28a745;
        }
        
        .widget-danger {
            border-left: 4px solid #dc3545;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(220, 53, 69, 0.1) 0%, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9) 100%);
        }
        
        .widget-danger .widget-icon {
            color: #dc3545;
        }
        
        .widget-danger .count {
            color: #dc3545;
        }
        
        .widget-warning {
            border-left: 4px solid #ffc107;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255, 193, 7, 0.1) 0%, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9) 100%);
        }
        
        .widget-warning .widget-icon {
            color: #ffc107;
        }
        
        .widget-warning .count {
            color: #ffc107;
        }
        
        .widget-info {
            border-left: 4px solid #17a2b8;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(23, 162, 184, 0.1) 0%, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9) 100%);
        }
        
        .widget-info .widget-icon {
            color: #17a2b8;
        }
        
        .widget-info .count {
            color: #17a2b8;
        }
        
        .widget-light {
            border-left: 4px solid #f8f9fa;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(248, 249, 250, 0.5) 0%, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9) 100%);
        }
        
        .widget-light .widget-icon {
            color: #6c757d;
        }
        
        .widget-light .count {
            color: #6c757d;
        }
        
        .widget-dark {
            border-left: 4px solid #343a40;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(52, 58, 64, 0.1) 0%, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9) 100%);
        }
        
        .widget-dark .widget-icon {
            color: #343a40;
        }
        
        .widget-dark .count {
            color: #343a40;
        }
        
        /* Responsive adjustments */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .widget {
                padding: 1rem;
            }
            
            .widget-icon {
                font-size: 2rem;
            }
            
            .widget-content .count {
                font-size: 1.5rem;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container mt-4">
        <h1>Widget Component Demo</h1>
        <p class="lead">Reusable Twig component aligned with the Enabel Bootstrap Theme Widget, using Symfony UX Icons.</p>
        
        <h2>Basic Usage</h2>
        <p>The Widget component can be used with minimal configuration:</p>
        
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-3">
                {{ component('Enabel:Ux:Widget', {
                    label: 'Projects',
                    count: '25',
                    variant: 'primary',
                    icon: 'lucide:folder'
                }) }}
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-3">
                {{ component('Enabel:Ux:Widget', {
                    label: 'Users',
                    count: '1,234',
                    variant: 'success',
                    icon: 'lucide:users'
                }) }}
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-3">
                {{ component('Enabel:Ux:Widget', {
                    label: 'Revenue',
                    count: '$45K',
                    variant: 'info',
                    icon: 'lucide:dollar-sign'
                }) }}
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-3">
                {{ component('Enabel:Ux:Widget', {
                    label: 'Orders',
                    count: '89',
                    variant: 'warning',
                    icon: 'lucide:shopping-cart'
                }) }}
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <h2>Linked Widgets</h2>
        <p>Widgets can be made clickable by adding a <code>link</code> parameter:</p>
        
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-3">
                {{ component('Enabel:Ux:Widget', {
                    label: 'View Projects',
                    count: '25',
                    variant: 'primary',
                    icon: 'lucide:external-link',
                    link: '/projects'
                }) }}
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-3">
                {{ component('Enabel:Ux:Widget', {
                    label: 'Manage Users',
                    count: '1,234',
                    variant: 'secondary',
                    icon: 'lucide:settings',
                    link: '/users'
                }) }}
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <h2>All Variants</h2>
        <p>The Widget component supports all Bootstrap color variants:</p>
        
        <div class="row">
            {% for variant in ['primary', 'secondary', 'success', 'danger', 'warning', 'info', 'light', 'dark'] %}
                <div class="col-md-3">
                    {{ component('Enabel:Ux:Widget', {
                        label: variant|title ~ ' Widget',
                        count: (loop.index * 10),
                        variant: variant,
                        icon: 'lucide:star'
                    }) }}
                </div>
            {% endfor %}
        </div>
        
        <h2>Without Count</h2>
        <p>Widgets can display just labels without numerical counts:</p>
        
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-4">
                {{ component('Enabel:Ux:Widget', {
                    label: 'Status: Active',
                    variant: 'success',
                    icon: 'lucide:check-circle'
                }) }}
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
                {{ component('Enabel:Ux:Widget', {
                    label: 'System Health',
                    variant: 'info',
                    icon: 'lucide:activity'
                }) }}
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
                {{ component('Enabel:Ux:Widget', {
                    label: 'Alerts: None',
                    variant: 'light',
                    icon: 'lucide:bell'
                }) }}
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <h2>Code Examples</h2>
        
        <h3>Basic Widget</h3>
        <pre><code>{{ "{{ component('Enabel:Ux:Widget', {
    label: 'Projects',
    count: '25',
    variant: 'primary',
    icon: 'lucide:folder'
}) }}" }}</code></pre>
        
        <h3>Linked Widget</h3>
        <pre><code>{{ "{{ component('Enabel:Ux:Widget', {
    label: 'View Projects',
    count: '25',
    variant: 'primary',
    icon: 'lucide:external-link',
    link: '/projects'
}) }}" }}</code></pre>
        
        <h3>Widget Without Count</h3>
        <pre><code>{{ "{{ component('Enabel:Ux:Widget', {
    label: 'Status: Active',
    variant: 'success',
    icon: 'lucide:check-circle'
}) }}" }}</code></pre>
        
        <h2>Configuration Options</h2>
        <table class="table table-striped">
            <thead>
                <tr>
                    <th>Property</th>
                    <th>Type</th>
                    <th>Default</th>
                    <th>Description</th>
                </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
                <tr>
                    <td><code>label</code></td>
                    <td>string</td>
                    <td>''</td>
                    <td>The text label displayed in the widget</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td><code>variant</code></td>
                    <td>string</td>
                    <td>'primary'</td>
                    <td>Color variant: primary, secondary, success, danger, warning, info, light, dark</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td><code>icon</code></td>
                    <td>string|null</td>
                    <td>null</td>
                    <td>Symfony UX Icons identifier (e.g., 'lucide:folder')</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td><code>link</code></td>
                    <td>string|null</td>
                    <td>null</td>
                    <td>URL to make the widget clickable</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td><code>count</code></td>
                    <td>string|null</td>
                    <td>null</td>
                    <td>Numerical or textual count to display</td>
                </tr>
            </tbody>
        </table>
    </div>
    
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>